Class GameNavigationPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node

    public class GameNavigationPane
extends FrontendPane
implements PlayerInputObserver
    Main screen of the front-end UI. Handles user input and presents the game catalog by relying on an object conforming to the GameNavigationLayout interface.
    Author:
    Thomas Debouverie

It is necessary to wait before laying out children, otherwise geometry of the pane is not yet ready for position and sizes calculations.
